msgctxt "340_Player"
msgid "(Boxcelios 2? Looks like an arcade shooter...)"
msgstr "(¿Boxcelios 2? Parece ser un shooter arcade...)"

msgctxt "352_Boxcelios 2"
msgid "The sequel to Boxcelios. Control an invincible fighter and destroy as many enemies as possible before time runs out. This time, the game takes place over land."
msgstr "La secuela de Boxcelios. Controla un invencible caza y destruye tantos enemigos sea posible antes que acabe el tiempo. Esta vez, el juego tiene lugar sobre la tierra."

msgctxt "364_Boxcelios 2"
msgid "Shoot and destroy either the glowing core or the majority of enemy ships to take them down."
msgstr "Dispara y destruye el núcleo brillante o la mayoría de las naves enemigas para acabar con ellas."

msgctxt "376_Boxcelios 2"
msgid "Time stands still for two seconds after an enemy appears. Use this time to aim for the enemy's core for maximum efficiency."
msgstr "Time stands still for two seconds after an enemy appears. Use this time to aim for the enemy's core for maximum efficiency."

msgctxt "400_Haruka"
msgid "Uncle Kaz! I want you to beat Level 20 in Boxelios 2! I know you can do it!"
msgstr "¡Tío Kaz! ¡Pasa el nivel 20 en Boxcelios 2! ¡Sé que puedes hacerlo!"

msgctxt "412_Kiryu"
msgid "(Beat Level 20 in Boxelios 2... One play is 100 yen. Should I give it a try?)"
msgstr "(Pasar el 20 en Boxcelios 2... Una partida cuesta 100 yenes. ¿Debería intentarlo?)."

msgctxt "436_Player"
msgid "All right, I'll give it a try."
msgstr "De acuerdo, lo intentaré."

msgctxt "448_Haruka"
msgid "Good luck, Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr "¡Buena suerte, Tío Kaz!"

msgctxt "472_Player"
msgid "(I don't have enough money...)"
msgstr "(No tengo suficiente dinero...)."

